# Operations & Recovery Implementation Plan

This plan outlines the implementation of the Organizer Live Dashboard, the Refund & Dispute Resolution System, and a robust Notification Engine.

## Proposed Changes

---

### [Database Schema]
Update the schema to support refunds, disputes, and notification tracking.

#### [MODIFY] [schema.prisma](file:///e:/et-ticket-app/services/api/prisma/schema.prisma)
- Add `RefundStatus` and `DisputeStatus` enums.
- Add `Refund` model linked to [Purchase](file:///e:/et-ticket-app/services/api/src/services/fraud.service.ts#89-119) and [Transaction](file:///e:/et-ticket-app/services/api/src/controllers/financial.controller.ts#64-86).
- Add `Dispute` model for tracking conflicts.
- Add `NotificationLog` model for audit trails.
- Add `RefundReason` and `DisputeSource` enums.

---

### [Organizer Dashboard]
Create a high-performance command center for event operations.

#### [NEW] [EventOperationsService](file:///e:/et-ticket-app/services/api/src/services/event-operations.service.ts)
- Implement methods for `getLiveSalesMetrics`, `getEntrySnapshot`, and `getPostEventSummary`.
- Use Redis to cache volatile metrics (entry rates, sales velocity).

#### [NEW] [OrganizerController](file:///e:/et-ticket-app/services/api/src/controllers/organizer.controller.ts)
- Secure endpoints for organizer-only visibility.
- Filter out sensitive fraud/security data (Risk Scores).

---

### [Refund & Dispute System]
Handle financial reversals and conflict resolution.

#### [NEW] [RefundService](file:///e:/et-ticket-app/services/api/src/services/refund.service.ts)
- `requestRefund`: validates eligibility (window, status).
- `processRefund`: handles ledger reversals and wallet deductions.
- `handleAutomaticRefunds`: triggered by event cancellation.

#### [NEW] [DisputeService](file:///e:/et-ticket-app/services/api/src/services/dispute.service.ts)
- Manages `OPEN`, `UNDER_REVIEW`, `RESOLVED` states.

---

### [Notification Engine]
A centralized, event-driven communication hub.

#### [MODIFY] [SmsService](file:///e:/et-ticket-app/services/api/src/services/sms.service.ts)
- Integrate AfroMessage for Ethiopia-specific SMS delivery.
- Add template support.

#### [NEW] [NotificationService](file:///e:/et-ticket-app/services/api/src/services/notification.service.ts)
- Abstract provider logic (SMS, Push, Email).
- Event-driven patterns (`notifyUser`, `alertAdmin`).

## System Architecture & Sequences

### 1. Ticket Purchase Flow
```mermaid
sequenceDiagram
    participant User
    participant App
    participant Payment
    participant Financial
    participant QR
    participant Notify

    User->>App: Choose Tickets
    App->>Payment: Initialize Payment
    Payment-->>User: Redirect to Gate
    User->>Payment: Complete Pay
    Payment->>App: Webhook / Success
    App->>Financial: Record Purchase
    Financial->>QR: Generate Signed QR
    QR-->>Notify: Send Confirmation (SMS)
    Notify-->>User: OTP/Ticket SMS
```

### 2. Refund Workflow
```mermaid
sequenceDiagram
    participant User
    participant Admin
    participant RefundSvc
    participant Wallet
    participant Gateway

    User->>RefundSvc: Request Refund
    RefundSvc->>RefundSvc: Eligibility Check
    RefundSvc->>Admin: Review Request
    Admin->>RefundSvc: Approve
    RefundSvc->>Gateway: Trigger Gateway Refund
    RefundSvc->>Wallet: Deduct Organizer
    Wallet-->>User: Notify
```

## Verification Plan

### Automated Tests
- `verify-refunds.ts`: Simulate cancellation and manual refund flows, checking ledger balances.
- `verify-dashboard.ts`: High-concurrency throughput testing for analytics dashboard.

### Manual Verification
- Testing SMS delivery via AfroMessage.
- Validating role-based access for Organizers vs Admins.
